The paper discusses a middleware system for scaling transactional databases, which involves topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC), database systems (cs.DB), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), software engineering (cs.SE), and systems and control (cs.SY). The abstract mentions replication algorithms, load balancing, and scalability, which are all relevant to these sub-categories.
